---
import SecondaryTitle from "../components/ui/SecondaryTitle.astro";
import Section from "../components/ui/Section.astro";
import TextWrapper from "../components/ui/TextWrapper.astro";
import Title from "../components/ui/Title.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Section>
    <Title>Privacy Policy</Title>

    <TextWrapper>
      <p>Last updated: November 3, 2025</p>

      <p>
        Thank you for visiting this website. Your privacy is important, and this
        page explains how your personal information is collected, used, and
        protected.
      </p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>1. Data Controller</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>The data controller responsible for this website is Anna Hilla.</p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>2. Information Collected</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>
        When you contact me through the contact form, I collect the following
        information:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc px-4">
        <li>Your name</li>
        <li>Your email address</li>
        <li>The message you send</li>
      </ul>

      <p>This information is voluntarily provided by you.</p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>3. Purpose of Data Processing</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>Your data is used <strong>solely</strong> for the purpose of:</p>

      <ul class="list-disc px-4">
        <li>Responding to your inquiry or message.</li>
        <li>Providing any information or assistance you requested.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Your personal data will <strong>not</strong> be used for marketing purposes
        or shared with third parties, unless legally required.
      </p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>4. Legal Basis</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>
        The legal basis for processing your personal data is your consent, which
        you give when submitting the contact form and accepting this privacy
        policy.
      </p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>5. Data Retention</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>
        Your personal data is stored only for as long as necessary to respond to
        your message and maintain basic communication records.
      </p>
      <p>Once it is no longer needed, it will be securely deleted.</p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>6. Data Security</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>
        All reasonable technical and organizational measures are taken to
        protect your data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.
      </p>
      <p>
        Email submissions may be processed through third-party email providers
        (e.g., Resend) used to deliver messages securely.
      </p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>7. Your Rights</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>
        Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the right
        to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc px-4">
        <li>Access your personal data.</li>
        <li>Request correction or deletion.</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time.</li>
        <li>
          File a complaint with a data protection authority if you believe your
          data has been misused.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>To exercise your rights, please contact me.</p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>8. Cookies and Analytics</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>
        This website does not use cookies for tracking, analytics, or
        advertising purposes.
      </p>
      <p>
        If third-party tools are added in the future, this policy will be
        updated accordingly.
      </p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>9. Changes to This Policy</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>
        This privacy policy may be updated from time to time to reflect changes
        in legal requirements or website functionality.
      </p>
      <p>The updated version will always be available on this page.</p>
    </TextWrapper>

    <TextWrapper>
      <SecondaryTitle>10. Contact</SecondaryTitle>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how your data is
        handled, please <a class="underline" href="/contact">contact me</a>.
      </p>
    </TextWrapper>
  </Section>
</Layout>
